}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== This thing uses '''''four''''' '''[[Alcor Micro]]''' AU6254 hub ICs. :The hub IC packages are marked with "'''ALCOR'''", "AU6254", "K41-JBL-NP", "H28922-0", and "0816TM".
This device presents itself to the host system as 4x 058f:6254 devices.
"RoHS", "2002/95/EC", "CP11 REV:B", and "MADE IN CHINA" is silkscreened on the board. :The capacitors are marked with '''S.I.'''.
The '''Manhattan''' 161022 would appear to be this device (or it is at least using the same shell)..
